the best sources he can gather.

911
00:57:21,963 --> 00:57:24,763
He brought Campbell
into the process...

912
00:57:24,833 --> 00:57:27,163
of looking at his work
on Star Wars...

913
00:57:27,233 --> 00:57:30,723
