''The costs are rising.
It's this, it's that.

1645
01:38:14,373 --> 01:38:16,603
Look, we've read drafts of scripts...

1646
01:38:16,683 --> 01:38:19,543
that make no sense to us
in any way, shape or form. ''

1647
