03:07:59,554 --> 03:08:01,074
I told you they'd do it.

3116
03:08:02,984 --> 03:08:08,124
But for George Lucas, completing
the trilogy involved personal sacrifice.

3117
03:08:08,794 --> 03:08:12,524
The success ofJedi
